      • getTargets

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<EEFWidgetDescription> getTargets()
        Returns the value of the 'Targets' reference list. The list contents are of type EEFWidgetDescription. It is bidirectional and its opposite is ' Property Validation Rules'. The widgets involved in this validation rule.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Targets' reference list.
